mesquite.lib

Class MesquiteParameter

  • java.lang.Object
    • mesquite.lib.MesquiteDouble
      • mesquite.lib.MesquiteParameter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Explainable, Listable

    public class MesquiteParameter
extends MesquiteDouble
implements Explainable
    An object to wrap a parameter used. New after 1. 12. Limited use; in future could replace many uses of MesquiteDouble for module parameters.
